data.description: You will love all the space and updates in this move in ready 4 bedroom Colonial 2 story home in Mayfair subdivision. Newly finished hardwood floors in dining room as well as the huge living room that also features a fireplace. New base trim throughout first floor.  Large eat-in kitchen with SGD to a huge  privacy fenced back yard. Fresh neutral carpet throughout second floor bedrooms, hallway, and stairs. Primary bedroom has large walk-in closet. Fresh paint throughout the home. Formal dining room could be a 5th bedroom. Both bathrooms fully updated with new vanities with granite tops, light fixtures, and new tile floors in both bathrooms, kitchen , and entry hallway. New light fixtures and fan in kitchen, dining room, and living room . New high efficiency furnace with paired central air system and power vented hot water heater.  Spacious full basement ready to finish, and a 2 car attached garage with pull down stairs to attic storage above. Move in ready!
